Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.12,0:01:57.11,OPCN-1,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur9}在夜里的海上闪耀着炮火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:02:01.90,OPCN-1,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur9}犹如无声的呐喊一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:05.79,OPCN-1,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur9}搜寻着最后的温存
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:08.82,OPCN-1,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur9}乘风破浪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:10.98,OPCN-1,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur9}梦中所见纯洁的AZUR
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:13.62,OPCN-1,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur9}请告诉越过痛苦的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:15.74,OPCN-1,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur9}究竟有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:18.63,OPCN-1,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur9}心中许下誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.75,0:02:20.90,OPCN-1,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur9}但愿这份坚强依旧温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.04,0:02:23.50,OPCN-1,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur9}无论何时都怀揣着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:25.70,OPCN-1,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur9}这份四散的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.88,0:02:30.38,OPCN-1,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur9}即便如此也要勇往直前
