Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.51,0:22:25.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur6}見つめ合うさざなみは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:31.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur6}君とかわすメッセージ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.43,0:22:38.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur6}この青い海でつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.14,0:22:43.39,EDJP,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur6}光の道標
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.06,0:22:49.75,EDJP,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur6}優しい人に出会えてるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.75,0:22:55.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur6}今笑えてるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.40,0:23:01.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur6}星明かり凪ぐ　寂し気な目に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:06.42,EDJP,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur6}輝きを満たして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:11.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur6}I'm close to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.98,0:23:17.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur6}いつもそばにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:22.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur6}明日が見えない夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:28.95,EDJP,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur6}心で呼びかけてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.63,0:23:34.07,EDJP,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur6}Please stay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:40.23,EDJP,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur6}どうか諦めずに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.57,0:23:49.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur6}いつか手を取り合える朝まで
