Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.43,0:22:38.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur9}在这片蔚蓝海上连接着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.14,0:22:43.39,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur9}光之信标
