Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.75,0:22:55.08,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur9}现在我依旧在笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.40,0:23:01.06,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur9}繁星照耀的寂寞眼瞳中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:06.42,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur9}充满着光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:11.60,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur9}我在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.98,0:23:17.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur9}永远在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:22.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur9}即便看不见明天的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:28.95,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur9}也会用心灵去呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.63,0:23:34.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur9}请留在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:40.23,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,300)\blur9}请不要放弃
